_mkboot_ - install and configure loader and the kernel on a device

_mkboot_ [-*rwsm01234*] *dev*

 -*01234*  limit the maximum number of hard drives
 -*r*      read-only root fs
 -*w*      read-write root fs
 -*s*      put the disks to sleep after 5 minutes of inactivity
 -*m*      monochrome (mode 7) display
